divs: sighting detailsi saw the star\light that the lady from lake jackson fl. saw past 2008-26-05. but i saw it 2008-27-05 at around 8:00pm et. i was looking at the sky and saw cloud movement and a star moving from west to east. i was in front of the hollywood fl. city hall at this coordinates 26.00'39.15'north 80.08'29.68'west. the object looked like a star and seamed to flight at very low speed above a 30,000 ft ceiling. it was visible for at least 5 minutes.
